data.description:
***Visit Our Open House this Sunday, January 21st from 3-4:30pm.***                                            

BETTER THAN NEW & PRICED BELOW CITY Appraised Value....Skip the hassles of building!  This home is loaded with upgrades.  Features include:  Custom Blinds, Maintenance Free Deck, Fence is already installed, lawn and landscaping are done!!    The spacious foyer welcomes you as enter this meticulously cared for home. The gas fireplace and floating shelves are a focal point in the living room. You'll love the quartz countertops, island and open floor concept.  Spacious primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom and walk-in-closet. All appliances are included! Heated garage.  This bright and sunny home is Move-In Ready! Schedule your private showing today and be WOWED!
